Revision history for Perl extension Verilog::Pli

The contributors that suggested a given feature are shown in [].

* Verilog::Pli 1.702 5/5/2005

**	NEWS is now renamed Changes, to support CPAN indexing. [Offer Kaye]

****	Fix memory leak in Verilog::Pli::Net  [Chris Gomez]

* Verilog::Pli 1.701 9/13/2004

****	Documentation fixes.

* Verilog::Pli 1.7 1/27/2004

****	Documentation fixes.

* Verilog::Pli 1.6 7/22/2003

***	Allow $NET{"%x:foo"} to return or set foo in hex format.
	Allow $NET{"foo"} = 0x#### to set foo in hex format

***	Allow reading and setting of wires.
	Note some simulators do not support forcing of wires.

* Verilog::Pli 1.5 8/30/2002

****	Update build for Perl 5.8.0

* Verilog::Pli 1.4 2/13/2001

****	Support for Verilator and other PLI headers

****	Documentation updates

* Verilog::Pli 1.3 1/21/2000

****	Support VCS 5.1 in example.

* Verilog::Pli 1.2 10/25/1999

**	First Announced CPAN Release

